projects.name: HOME HARBOR (MernStack)
projects.description: The application facilitates the buying and renting of houses and apartments. It incorporates the latest version of React Router DOM for seamless navigation and employs JSON web tokens for authentication, including Google Auth integration. This project allows user to search and buy home according to their preferences and also users are able to upload the home for rental purpose. This main purpose of this project is to provide home searching under their fingertip which reduce their time and cost.
